description: Try our easy to follow Mini Frittatas recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Mini Frittatas Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Bake for 30 minutes or until golden and set. Stand for 5 minutes before removing from the tray, then transfer to a wire rack to cool. Garnish with parsley. Wrap frittatas in plastic wrap and pack into lunch boxes.
